text: Office building with retail & F&B shops on levels B1, 1 & 2. The office lobby is on level 2. A vibrant building with lots of history, Clifford Centre is also conveniently located right at Raffles Place MRT.
Clean and comfortable. There are public transportations around here. The bicycle is free to use and the bus is very useful for the tourists.
Here for lunch at NTUC Foodfare located at Basement 1. Wide range of food available at reasonable prices.

Not very cohesive environment for the dining at the first floor. 3 stalls, 3 different seating partition. If you buy from one and sit at the other, the cleaner will knock on the table to ask you to MOVE... NOW... like in military. Please keep your cool or police will get involved. So much for racial harmony...
